*Ostanem* sama kući (I will stay home alone).
Krenuću u šetnju, a *ostaću* tu dok se ne vratim (I will go for a walk and *stay* here until I come back).
On nikad neće dozvoliti da *ostanem* sam (He will never allow me to *stay* alone).
Nisam *ostala* bez para nakon posete tržnom centru (I did not *stay* without money after visiting the mall).
*Ostanite* tu još nekoliko minuta (*Stay* here for a few more minutes).